== Ubuzima bwa Ndimbati muri make ==
'''Ndimbati''' ni Umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye Nyarusange  mu [[Akarere ka Muhanga|karere ka Muhanga]], muri 1989 akiri urubyiruko yaje kwimukira mu  [[Burundi]] na [[Uganda]] aza kugaruka mu [[Rwanda]] nyuma ya 1994<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/ndimbati-wo-muri-papa-sava-yagize-icyo-asaba-abanyarwanda-nyuma-y-amashusho</ref>. Ubwo ndimbati yari muri [[Uganda]] yaje kwinjira mu Gisirikare ariko asubira mubuzima busanzwe muri 1999.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-52126748</ref> ndimbati ubu afite umugore  yashatse mbere y'uko ajya mu gisirikare kandi niwe bakibana bafitanye  n'abana <ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/228237</ref><ref>https://ukwezi.rw/Imyidagaduro/article/Ndimbati-yariye-indimi-abajijwe-ipeti-yakuye-mu-gisirikare</ref>

